200.d0              R_0    - position of cyclotron resonance point, cm
2.d4                B0     - magnetic field at the resonant point, G
0.03d0              gam    - angle between mag. field and Z-axis
1                   isort  - resonant minority (1 - hydrogen, 2 - deuterium)
5d13                den    - electron density cm^{-3}
0.2                 conc   - minority concentration
4.d5                anu_e  - electron collision frequency
1.d4                anu_h  - hydrogen collision frequency
1.d4                anu_d  - deuterium collision frequency
3.d3                T_e    - electron temperature
3.d3                T_h    - hydrogen temperature
3.d3                T_d    - deuterium temperature
